Fortis to Consolidate India, International Operations, CNBC Says

-- B y   P r a d e e p   K u r u p
-- 
2011-09-19T05:21:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/fortis-to-consolidate-india-international-operations-cnbc-says.html
Fortis Healthcare Ltd. (FORH)  plans to
consolidate its Indian and international operations, CNBC TV-18
reported today, without saying where it got the information.  Fortis will acquire the international unit in an all-cash
deal, according to the report.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
